name: train production, passenger, high speed | train, passenger, high speed | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/8715/documentation

The dataset represents the production of a high speed train.

Service starts with the material consumption for the production of the high speed train.

The dataset ends with the production of one high speed train. The dataset includes material consumption, transport, energy and fuel consumption. The disposal of the high speed train is included as well.
category: C:Manufacturing/30:Manufacture of other transport equipment/302:Manufacture of railway locomotives and rolling stock/3020:Manufacture of railway locomotives and rolling stock

processDocumentation.geographyDescription: Manufacturing data represents a train produced in Germany.
processDocumentation.technologyDescription: Train manufacturing data is available from Rozycki (2003) mainly based on (Maibach, 1999). ;References:;Maibach M., Peter D. and Seiler B. (1999) Ökoinventar Transporte: Grundlagen für den ökologischen Vergleich von Transportsystemen und den Einbezug von Transportsystemen in Ökobilanzen. Technischer Schlussbericht. In: Schweizerischer Nationalfonds zur Förderung der wissenschaftlichen Forschung (ed. SPP Umwelt M.). 2nd Edition. INFRAS, Zürich;von Rozycki C., Koeser H. and Schwarz H. (2003) Ecology Profile of the German High-speed Rail Passenger Transport System, ICE. In: International Journal of Life Cycle Assessment, 8(2), pp. 83-91.
processDocumentation.samplingDescription: The data of the material composition and energy consumption is based on  literature studies.
